      <b>
       lttng g f dsrs
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       W ll hv dsrs – t’s prt f th hmn cndtn.
      </p>
      <p>
       W wnt t b lvd, t hv frnds, t xprnc jy, t hv scrty.
      </p>
      <p>
       Bt  dsr fr
       <em>
        thngs
       </em>
       s nt s ntrl s w’r ftn ld t blv. Sr, w ll hv dsrs fr thngs: nc crs, nc clths, nc hss, cl cmptrs nd Phns, btfl frntr nd ntbks nd shs nd jwlry nd bgs nd bks nd n nd n.
      </p>
      <p>
       Bt ths dsrs r mnfctrd n s, by dvrtsng nd mrktng. Thy ply n r ntrl nstncts: fr hrdng (scrty), fr th plsrs f fd nd drgs nd sx (dsr fr jy), fr fttng n wth clths nd bks nd gdgts (dsr fr frnds), nd s n.
      </p>
      <p>
       Dsrs lk ths ld t ll knds f prblms — n fct, ll th prblms f mdrn scty. Thy r rtd n th mmns pwr f crprtns n r scty, nd thr drv fr mssv prfts. Prblms rslt tht ncld bsty nd rltd dsss, mssv cnsmr dbt, shllw cnsmrsm, vrwrk (t mk mny fr ll ths thngs), lck f tr hmn cnnctn, nd mr.
      </p>
      <p>
       And whl dsrs r prfctly ntrl nd nvdbl, f w cn lrn t lt g f th mnfctrd dsrs, w’ll strt t fr rslvs frm th chns f cnsmrsm.
      </p>
      <p>
       Strt t bcm wr f ths dsrs – rcgnz thr sgns n y. Ps bfr ctng n thm. Tk dp brths, g fr  wlk, gt sm prspctv. Y dn’t rlly nd mr thngs, nd byng s nt th nswr. Mk d wtht nd fnd hppnss wtht mr stff.
      </p>
      <p>
       Lt th dsr g, nd fl th lghtnss, th frdm. Bcm lbrtd frm dsrs, n t  tm (nt frvr, bt fr th mmnt). Y’ll lv t.
      </p>
